Metropolitan;;85;;93;;PG-13;;A radical student is adopted by a group of young New Yorkers, serves as a catalyst to alter his and their lives. Gathering in a Manhattan apartment, the group of friends meet to discuss social mobility, Fourier's socialism and play bridge in their cocoon of upper-class society - until they are joined by a man with a critical view of their way of life.;;Comedy,Drama;;Whit Stillman;;1990;;Carolyn Farina,Edward Clements,Chris Eigeman,Taylor Nichols,Allison Parisi,Dylan Hundley,Isabel Gillies,Bryan Leder,Will Kempe,Ellia Thompson;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/metropolitan